### Task Management API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Upload Excel File - Chat Evaluation
POST {{baseUrl}}/rest/api/v1/tasks
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary123

--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="chat-evaluation-QnA.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

< ./data/chat-evaluation-QnA.xlsx
--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="task_type"

chat-evaluation
--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Chat evaluation API test upload
--boundary123--

