###

### List All Tasks (First Page)
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/api/v1/tasks?per_page=20&task_type=chat-evaluation
Accept: application/json

###

### List Tasks with Smaller Page Size
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/api/v1/tasks?per_page=2&task_type=chat-evaluation
Accept: application/json

###

### List Next Page Using Cursor (replace "12" with actual next_cursor from previous response)
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/api/v1/tasks?per_page=2&task_type=chat-evaluation&cursor=12
Accept: application/json

###

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Application Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/info
Accept: application/json

###

### H2 Database Console (GET request to check availability)
GET {{baseUrl}}/h2-console
Accept: text/html

###

### Get Available Task Types
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/api/v1/task/types
Accept: application/json

